						"description": "Poll payment status from the frontend using the Paymob `client_secret` parameter.\n\n### Implementation Details:\n- Endpoint: `GET /api/payments/verify/{clientSecret}`\n- How it works: Queries the Paymob elements API under the hood to check if the student paid successfully, updates the local database status, and advances the application to `approved` if paid.\n- Safe for frontend polling after redirection."
